title: New Music: Steel Panther Premieres 'Poontang Boomerang' Video [News]
text:
UG News editor since early 2013. King Crimson fan. I handle the news around here. Posted 12 hours ago 8 
Steel Panther has unveiled "Poontang Boomerang" as a new video single off their upcoming fourth major-label album "Lower the Bar," due out on March 24 via Kobalt Music Recordings. 
According to the press release, "the clip explores the true meaning of 'not sticking your dude piston in crazy.'" 
You can check it out in the embedded player below.
